overview: The user requested a thorough browser-based test of the sleep
  questionnaire application. The agent started by navigating the main
  questionnaire flow, attempting to fill out sections and test validation. It
  then utilized a developer "Pre-fill & Jump to Report" button to quickly test
  the report generation and successfully verified the PDF download
  functionality. Subsequently, the agent tested the admin login, confirming that
  it was protected and that error handling for incorrect passwords worked as
  expected. A key finding was that the "Next Section" button on the introductory
  page failed to navigate, despite the alerts being informational rather than
  validation-related, indicating a potential issue with the application's
  navigation logic.
